title: Mawaqit
about_us:
Mawaqit is a non-profit project. It is for god’s sake (WAQF fi sabil Allah).
It is and always will be completely FREE and WITHOUT ANY ADS.

We provide you with the PRECISE timetables as set by your mosque managers. Unlike other apps that provides you with approximations.
